      .whiteTxt
        p Located in Portland, Oregon since 2009, <i>Interactive Balance</i> has been building custom online training software to large scale corporations worldwide. We changed the way HR does business by creating a system allowing delegation from corporate to regions to properties, instead of a single HR unit managing hundreds of thousands of records.  Everyone is responsible for their own department.
        p <large>99%</large> of our work is proprietary so we can't show any of it on the open web, but please set up a demo any time and we'll run you through the applications.
        a.button.small(href='mailto:info@interactivebalance.com') Request a Show
        h2.whiteTxt Industries we've built systems for:
        ul.margin-bull
          li Dealerships
          li Hosptiality parent corporations
          li International Furnitur and Textile Centers
        p We welcome other projects, mainly data centric in need of some organization, designs and on the fly chartings.

